headline.main: Conte Demands Champions League Diet for Chelsea
headline.print_headline: Conte Demands Champions League Diet for Chelsea

lead_paragraph: Chelsea manager Antonio Conte hates not being in the Champions League and has made it his mission to ensure the Premier League leaders consistently qualify for Europe's elite competition.
